Name: China Shengda Packaging Group Inc
Description: DELISTED - China Shengda Packaging Group Inc. is a paper packaging company in China. Through its wholly owned subsidiaries, Great Shengda, Shengda Color, Hangzhou Shengming and Suzhou AA, the Company is principally engaged in the design, manufacture and sale of flexo-printed and color-printed corrugated paper cartons in a range of sizes and strengths. The Company also manufactures corrugated paperboards, which are used for the production of its flexo-printed and color-printed cartons. The Company provides paper packaging solutions to a range of industries, including food, beverage, machinery and other consumer or industrial sectors. Its products are single-layer paper cartons for food, double-layer paper cartons for garments, chemicals, furniture, and triple-layer paper cartons for electrical machinery, motorcycles, and other heavy-duty products. On September 22, 2011, it incorporated Jiangsu Shuangsheng Paper Technology Development CO., Ltd. in Jiangsu Province, the People's Republic of China.
